    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1908-11-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1908-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="210"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d210">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President-elect <persName type="from">Gomez</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Allow me to express to you our congratulations and heartfelt thanks for the
                    absolute impartiality, tact, and ableness observed by Governor Magoon and
                    subordinates during the elections, thus giving the people of Cuba an opportunity
                    to cast their votes with entire liberty.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">José Miguel Gomez.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
